        "body": "Closes #113\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\nAdds a fully functional Contact Us page at `/contact`.\r\n\r\n## What was added\r\n- Responsive form with Name, Email, Subject, and Message fields\r\n- Client-side validation on required fields\r\n- Formspree integration for email delivery (no backend needed)\r\n- Loading state on submit button\r\n- Success and error messages after submission\r\n- Matches KisanAI dark theme with green accents\r\n\r\n## Related issue\r\n- Closes #113\r\n\r\n## Type of change\r\n- [x] New feature\r\n\r\n## Files added\r\n- `src/app/contact/page.jsx`\r\n\r\n## Screenshots\r\n<img width=\"1512\" height=\"982\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-23 at 3 55 58 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/286e076f-ce63-48c7-9628-1d6eb8178d3c\" />\r\n",
